<div class="story flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-center items-center gap-8 lg:gap-4 w-[95%] lg:w-[65%] mx-auto">
	<div class="basis-1/2">
		<video autoplay loop muted class="w-full h-full object-cover min-h-[400px]">
			<source src="./Images/noithat.mp4">
		</video>
	</div>

	<div class="basis-1/2 text-center lg:text-left lg:pl-6">
		<div class="text-3xl leading-10 mb-6 ">What is your most special interior?</div>
		<div class="text-gray-500 leading-7 mb-6 text-justify">
			In an old house hidden in the middle of a water forest, the interior is meticulously and delicately presented, creating a cozy and luxurious space. Right from the main door, you are received by a small hallway with vintage paintings hanging on the wall, creating a blend of classic and modern beauty.
			The living room is a big focal point with the wall divided into small wooden squares, creating a unique geometric harmony. The paintings or artistic figurines that stand out on the wooden shelves are meticulously created. The brown cowhide sofa creates an impressive accent, combined with the classic wooden chairs upholstered in soft silk.
		</div>
		<div>
			<button type="button" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-200 to-blue-200 hover:from-pink-200 hover:to-yellow-300 ... font-medium ">
				Read the full Story
			</button>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
